data.description: Look no further, as this ranch-style epitomizes comfort and convenience. Boasting three spacious bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms, along with a two-car garage, this residence offers ample space for a growing family or those seeking room to relax. Step into the inviting living room with a cozy fire place, perfect for gathering with loved ones. The Owner's Suite provides a sanctuary of it's own, featuring a separate shower and tub, as well as generous walk-in-closet. Enjoy the serene outdoors situated on a corner lot. With all appliances, including the year old stainless steel refrigerator and stove. This home welcomes you with open arms.
